/** Creature  **/
@?alive  // need this?
@health
@speed
@position
@line of site (LOS)

/**  Human : Creature  **/
@?alive = true
@defense // ?
@?bit
@meat

if lower health, speed --


/**  Runner : Human  **/
@speed ++
@carry capacity = can carry  1-n cargo// possible upgrade
	for each cargo*:
		LOS --
		speed --
	

/**  Guard : Human  **/
@defense ++
@weapon*


/**  Zombie : Creature  **/
@?alive = false
@hearing distance
@armReach
@changeDirectionCountdown

if human in armReach, grab
if contact human, bite
if contact dead human, eat #? human.meat
if human in LOS, move toward human.position 
				 changeDirectionCountdown = 0
if hear sound, move towards sound
				changeDirectionCountdown = 0
if hit obstacle 
	if changeDirectionCountdown = #?, change direction
	else, changeDirectionCountdown ++

else, move forward


/**  Weapon  **/
@damage
@range
@precision

